item.title: About
item.description: Hi there, I’m Julia. I’m a developer and artist living a peaceful life in a small town called Rishikesh, located in foothills of the Indian Himalayas. I completed my bachelors in Computer Engineering, and after 5 years working as the Director of Technology in a Medical Education start up, I decided to take my work in the direction of my childhood passion - creating video games. I’ve been making art my whole life and really enjoy the combination of the technical structure in game algorithms and the creativity expression & freedom of art and animation in a game.
